stories.title: 'Day-night matches unfair': Lara
stories.subTitle: South Africa v West Indies, 4th ODI, Centurion
stories.summary: Brian Lara was quick to point out the ills of day-night matches after West Indies convincingly beat South Africa in a day game at Centurion to register their first win of the five-match one-day series

stories.title: West Indies race to astonishing victory
stories.subTitle: South Africa v West Indies, 4th ODI, Centurion
stories.summary: Last week, West Indies were bundled out for 54 and seemed already to be sitting on a beach back home, resting up ahead of the England series
stories.byline: The Wisden Bulletin by Andrew Miller
